================================================================================
                                PROJECT OVERVIEW
================================================================================

This software, "The Cosmic Davis 12D Hebbian Transformer," represents a 
foundational breakthrough in artificial intelligence and cognitive computing 
architectures. Developed and pioneered by Cory Shane Davis, these methods predate 
all comparable models worldwide, formally documented and archived on Zenodo.

Key Features & Innovations:
- 12-Dimensional Hebbian Learning: Advanced multidimensional neural weight 
  adjustments enabling unprecedented pattern recognition and cognitive plasticity.
- Cosmos Synaptic Swarm Orchestrator: Dynamic multi-agent harmonization for 
  complex task delegation and execution.
- Quantum Integration: First-of-its-kind structural links to quantum states 
  for non-deterministic decision matrices.
- Total Autonomous Agency: Fully integrated web platforms and 
  automated cross-platform social logic (X/Twitter, Autogram, etc.).
- Continuous Biological Learning Simulator: True AI evolution mimicking biological 
  growth patterns, synapses, and dynamic emotional states natively.

